item.title: About
item.description: Dora Designs is located in beautiful Mount Dora, Fl. just outside of Orlando. We service all of Central Florida, including: Sanford, Lake Mary, Apopka, Oviedo, Winter Park, Maitland, Altamonte, Ocoee, Winter Garden, Clermont, Minneola, Leesburg, Tavares, and The Villages. Capabilities/equipment Our current equipment includes: 4’x8’ 3-axis CNC router (3hp ER20 spindle, air&coolant mist, external dust collection) 4’x3’ 2.5-axis CNC Laser (150W CO2, Rotary attachments, external air extraction, 4 sided pass thru’s to handle larger workpieces) Trailblazer 325 welder for fabrication & backup power generation 7’x12’ Flatbed Truck for easy pickup and delivery of larger product 1400lb forklift for loading/unloading large workpieces and material pallets supporting manual cutting/drilling/sanding and QC inspection equipment COMING SOON!
